### ========================================
### EMPLOYEE MANAGEMENT API — HTTP Client
### ========================================

### [1] Hello — kiểm tra server chạy
GET http://localhost:8080/api/hello
Accept: application/json

###

### [2] Get ALL employees
GET http://localhost:8080/api/employees
Accept: application/json

###

### [3] Get employees — filter theo department
GET http://localhost:8080/api/employees?department=Engineering
Accept: application/json

###

### [4] Get employee by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/employees/1
Accept: application/json

###

### [5] Search — tìm theo tên HOẶC phòng ban
GET http://localhost:8080/api/employees/search?keyword=nguyen
Accept: application/json

###

### [6] Create employee mới
POST http://localhost:8080/api/employees
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "hoang van em",
  "email": "em.hoang@company.com",
  "position": "DevOps Engineer",
  "salary": 28000000,
  "departmentId": 1
}

###

### [7] Update employee
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/employees/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "salary": 35000000,
  "position": "Senior Backend Developer"
}

###

### [8] Delete employee
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/employees/4
Accept: application/json

###

### [9] Get ALL departments
GET http://localhost:8080/api/departments
Accept: application/json

###

### [10] Create department mới
POST http://localhost:8080/api/departments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Marketing",
  "description": "Marketing and communications"
}

###

### [11] Demo BCrypt hash
GET http://localhost:8080/api/demo/hash?password=mySecret123
Accept: application/json

###

### ── ERROR CASES ──────────────────────────────────

### [12] Validation error — thiếu field bắt buộc
POST http://localhost:8080/api/employees
Content-Type: application/json

{}

###

### [13] Not Found — ID không tồn tại
GET http://localhost:8080/api/employees/999
Accept: application/json

###

### [14] Search — keyword quá ngắn
GET http://localhost:8080/api/employees/search?keyword=a
Accept: application/json
